profile:
Our Experience:

Robert Fliesser is a veteran of the Canadian Armed Forces who retired to pursue his passion, woodworking. He is an honors graduate of the Algonquin College Cabinetry and Furniture Program, now working full time at custom woodworking and fine carpentry. 

***

Our Process:

Rob will come to your home and provide a free consultation and quote on any project.  Prior to starting construction full design drawings and selections of materials and finishes will be provided to ensure we meet your expectations.

***

Our Pledge: 

The Customer will drive the design and aesthetic for the project to suit their personal tastes and decor.   Customer satisfaction guaranteed or you do not take delivery of the project.  Quality of workmanship is fully guaranteed.

profile:
Greyhorne Interiors is Ottawa's newest modern furniture store.  From solid walnut dining tables to down-filled sofas, they have what you need to fill your contemporary space.

Owner James Flynn opened Greyhorne as a means of bringing high-end designer furniture to Ottawa. "You won't find salespeople here, just real people who love good design", say James.
Each piece they carry is fully customizable to suit your needs in your choice of wood species and size to your preference of leather or fabric.  
Every brand is carefully selected from Team 7 in Austria, Artifort from Holland, or Carl Hansen and Eilersen from Denmark.  All pieces are authentic designs from the best craftspeople the world has ever seen.

Price range - Medium to High

http://www.greyhorne.com
